svg></a></li></ul><div class=" fade fade-left faded"></div><div class=" fade fade-right"></div></div><section class="tab-content"><section><div class=" project-description"><h2><strong>Music Duration Reducer, hearing more of the amazing OST!<br></strong></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>This mod can do one simple thing, make music play more often in Minecraft! This mod can also change the pitch of music randomly. These settings are turned off by default but they are in the experimental section of the config.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you want to talk to me personally, come to <a href="https://discord.gg/bbhS2vy" rel="nofollow">my Discord server.</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can configure the options in your config folder, under 'musicdr.json'. Or, with Modmenu. For forge, its 'musicdr-client.toml'.</p>
<p>You can change the min and max delays (in seconds), or choose to divide the delays instead of setting your own. You can also toy around with the experimental settings and mess with pitch. How low and high it can randomly be, and how often it actually changes pitch.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><strong>Important</strong></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>There are two different versions, <strong>forge</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>fabric</strong>, and <strong>quilt</strong>. make sure you get the right version when downloading. 1.19.2 only has <strong>forge</strong> and <strong>quilt</strong>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><strong>FAQ</strong></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Will you move this to x.xx.xx version?</strong></p>
<p>No.</p>
<p><strong>How do I play this mod, it won't load for me!</strong></p>
<p>Make sure you either have forge or fabric depending on whatever one you're using. look it up if you're unsure what to do!</p></div></section><section class="project-team"><h2>The Music Duration Reducer Team</h2><div class="author"><div class="avatar-container"><img id="row-image" alt="profile avatar" loading="lazy" width="120" height="120" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="profile-avatar-image" style="color:transparent" src="https://static-cdn.jtvnw.net/jtv_user_pictures/4113dd1a-f020-4be4-ae68-8dd895f137b0-profile_image-150x150.png"/></div><div class="author-info"><div class="author-header-container"><div class="name-and-tags"><div class="author-name"><a aria-label="View LudoCrypt&#x27;s profile" href="/members/ludocrypt">LudoCrypt</a></div><div class="author-tags"><div class=" tag new-tag reversed">Owner</div></div></div></div><div class="author-description"><ul class="details"><li><div class="amount">170</div><div class="title">Followers</div></li><li><div class="amount">18</div><div class="title">Projects</div></li><li><div class="amount">5.1M</div><div class="title">Downloads</div></li></ul></div></div><div class="author-buttons"><button class=" btn-secondary btn-follow followed"><svg id="icon-heart" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.6941 16.9374C9.62723 16.9127 9.53909 16.8717 9.49824 16.8463C9.42695 16.802 8.95707 16.3331 8.09859 15.4496C7.87709 15.2216 7.51874 14.8535 7.30226 14.6316C7.08578 14.4097 6.37073 13.6734 5.71326 12.9954C4.58389 11.8845 3.25642 10.4905 2.48892 9.36636C2.13406 8.65228 1.99699 8.02266 2.0228 7.22523C2.03618 6.81185 2.07224 6.5603 2.16992 6.19884C2.5997 4.60848 3.87669 3.40511 5.47619 3.08321C5.70034 3.0381 5.80914 3.03061 6.24425 3.03031C6.68463 3.03 6.78594 3.03699 7.01613 3.08359C7.36409 3.15403 7.7708 3.29157 8.05941 3.4364C8.60401 3.70969 8.8496 3.90051 9.48306 4.54257L10.003 5.06955L10.4969 4.56536C11.1428 3.90603 11.3875 3.71377 11.9217 3.44582C12.2282 3.29213 12.6291 3.15542 12.9839 3.08359C13.2141 3.03699 13.3154 3.03 13